images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0835.JPG" rel="kurban-2013">      <img class="fancy-gallery" src="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0835.JPG" alt="" />    </a>    <a href="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0837.JPG" rel="kurban-2013">      <img class="fancy-gallery" src="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0837.JPG" alt="" />    </a>  </li>  <li>    <a href="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0840.JPG" rel="kurban-2013">      <img class="fancy-gallery" src="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0840.JPG" alt="" />    </a>    <a href="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0843.JPG" rel="kurban-2013">      <img class="fancy-gallery" src="images/rashod/kurban-2013/IMG_0843.JPG" alt="" />    </a>  </li></ul><p> Так же предлагаем к вашему просмотру небольшое видео праздничного намаза<br><a class="fancy-video-js" href="http://www.youtube.com/v/MoMHxfxNqnI&fs=1&amp;autoplay=1"><img style="width: 300px; height: 240px; padding-left: 120px;" src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/MoMHxfxNqnI/2.jpg" /></a>',
